data.text: Hey and Associates, Inc. would like to welcome Ben Gordon to our team. Ben is a 2019 graduate of the Georgia Institute of Technology with a BS in Environmental Engineering. After a time interning with our friends at the @Lake Forest Open Lands Association, Ben will be a perfect addition to our interdisciplinary team. He will be assisting our environmental scientists with on the ground restoration work and also applying his engineering degree assisting on a range of other studies and projects. Welcome aboard Ben!
